These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: hiking, reading, skydiving, writing
House: colonial, modern, art-deco, cape-cod
There are 4 different favourite colors: pink, green, blood-red, ebony
1. the person who likes pink is the person who's hobby is writing##1
2. the person who likes blood-red is on the left of the modern house##1
3. the person who's hobby is writing is in an odd position##4
4. the person who likes green is on the left or right of the person who likes ebony##3
5. the art-deco house is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is hiking##3
6. the person who likes ebony is on the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
7. the person who likes green is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person who likes ebony is between the cape-cod house and the person who's hobby is hiking##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |   2    |    3    |     4     |
| Hobby         | writing      | hiking | reading | skydiving |
| House   | art-deco | colonial  | modern   | cape-cod    |
| Color     | pink     | blood-red    | ebony    | green      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: dancing, singing, sudoku, video-games
There 4 different types of food: spinach, pepper, broccoli, cabbage
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, r&b, house, dubstep
1. the fan of r&b is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##3
2. the person who's hobby is video-games is the person eating broccoli##1
3. the person who's hobby is sudoku is in an even position##4
4. the fan of country is on the far right##1
5. the fan of dubstep is on the far left##1
6. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left of the person eating pepper##1
7. the person eating spinach is between the person who's hobby is video-games and the person who's hobby is singing##2
8. the person eating cabbage is between the person eating pepper and the person who's hobby is sudoku##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |    3    |    4     |
| Hobby         | video-games | sudoku   | singing | dancing  |
| Food   | broccoli     | spinach | cabbage  | pepper |
| Music-Genre     | dubstep        | house  | r&b    | country |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-3::.
There 4 different types of food: grapefruit, kiwi, lemon, tomato
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: january, june, july, november
House: wooden, cape-cod, modern, townhouse
1. the person who's birthday is in november is between the person eating grapefruit and the person eating tomato##2
2. the person who's birthday is in june is the townhouse house##1
3. the wooden house is the person eating lemon##1
4. the wooden house is on the right of the person eating tomato##1
5. the person eating tomato is in an odd position##4
6. the person who's birthday is in july is between the person eating kiwi and the person who's birthday is in january##2
7. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the modern house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4     |
| Food          | grapefruit | kiwi   | tomato     | lemon     |
| Birthday   | june  | november | july   | january  |
| House     | townhouse      | cape-cod | modern | wooden |

