.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-4::.
There are 4 different nationalities: pakistani, american, malaysian, thai
House: townhouse, modern, farmhouse, colonial
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, rowing, tennis, water-polo
1. the colonial house is in an even position##4
2. the american is the person who's sport is rowing##1
3. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1
4. the modern house is on the left or right of the malaysian##3
5. the colonial house is the person who's sport is badminton##1
6. the malaysian is the townhouse house##1
7. the farmhouse house is the pakistani##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Nationality   | pakistani  | thai   | malaysian     | american |
| House   | farmhouse  | colonial      | townhouse        | modern     |
| Sport         | tennis | badminton | water-polo | rowing   |

