.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-5::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: orchid, poppy, rose, bellflower
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: golf, rugby, swimming, volleyball
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, lemonade, juice, fanta
1. the person who growsbellflower is the person who's sport is volleyball##1
2. the person who growsrose is in an odd position##4
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the person who's sport is volleyball##1
4. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
5. the person drinking hot-chocolate is in an even position##4
6. the person who's sport is rugby is on the far left##1
7. the person who growspoppy is on the far right##1
8. the person who growsrose is on the left or right of the person drinking juice##3
9. the person who's sport is golf is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3     |    4     |
| Flower   | orchid   | bellflower   | rose | poppy |
| Sport         | rugby      | volleyball | golf      | swimming |
| Beverage     | lemonade | hot-chocolate        | fanta       | juice  |

