.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-6::.
There 4 different types of food: apricot, kiwi, lemon, pepper
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, tulip, daffodil, orchid
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, tram, van, snowmobile
1. the person eating kiwi is in an odd position##4
2. the person driving the van is on the right of the person who growsdaffodil##1
3. the person driving the bike is the person eating kiwi##1
4. the person eating lemon is on the left of the person driving the tram##1
5. the person who growstulip is on the far right##1
6. the person eating pepper is on the left of the person eating kiwi##1
7. the person eating pepper is in an even position##4
8. the person who growsorchid is on the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2      |     3      |    4    |
| Food    | lemon   | pepper      | kiwi       | apricot |
| Flower   | balloon-flower | orchid | daffodil     | tulip |
| Transport     | snowmobile     | tram  | bike | van |

