.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-7::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: coral, mauve, blue, azure
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: comedy, martial-arts, satire, time-travel
4 different games are played: bridge, chess, mah-jongg, poker
1. the person playing mah-jongg is the person watching comedy movies##1
2. the person playing chess is between the person watching time-travel movies and the person playing bridge##2
3. the person watching time-travel movies is the person who likes mauve##1
4. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left or right of the person who likes mauve##3
5. the person who likes coral is in an even position##4
6. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the person who likes azure##1
7. the person watching comedy movies is the person who likes coral##1
8. the person playing mah-jongg is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |       3       |     4      |
| Color      | blue   | azure          | mauve | coral        |
| Movie-Genre   | satire     | martial-arts | time-travel   | comedy     |
| Game           | bridge | chess         | poker         | mah-jongg |

