.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-8::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: march, december, january, july
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, fanta, lemonade, cola
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, disco, electronic, house
1. the fan of house is on the left or right of the fan of electronic##3
2. the person drinking lemonade is the person who's birthday is in march##1
3. the person drinking cola is the person who's birthday is in january##1
4. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the fan of electronic##1
5. the fan of disco is between the person drinking 7up and the person who's birthday is in march##2
6. the fan of house is on the left or right of the person drinking lemonade##3
7. the person who's birthday is in march is in an even position##4
8. the person who's birthday is in march is between the person who's birthday is in december and the person who's birthday is in january##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |     4      |
| Birthday         | december | march      | january       | july    |
| Beverage           | fanta  | lemonade  | cola | 7up |
| Music-Genre   | house      | electronic | disco         | country    |

