.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-9::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: yellow, red, azure, ivory
The people have 4 different jobs:  entrepreneur, manager, pilot, social-worker
There 4 different types of food: corn, apple, pumpkin, cucumber
1. the entrepreneur is in an odd position##4
2. the person who likes yellow is on the left or right of the entrepreneur##3
3. the person who likes ivory is on the left or right of the entrepreneur##3
4. the person eating apple is on the left of the person who likes yellow##1
5. the person who likes red is on the left or right of the person eating pumpkin##3
6. the person eating cucumber is on the right of the entrepreneur##1
7. the entrepreneur is on the right of the person who likes yellow##1
8. the manager is on the left of the person who likes azure##1
9. the social-worker is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |      3       |       4       |
| Color   | red         | yellow  | azure     | ivory         |
| Job        | social-worker | manager | entrepreneur | pilot         |
| Food      | apple         | pumpkin  | corn   | cucumber |

