.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-10::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: lavender, fuchsia, brown, mauve
The people have 4 different jobs:  teacher, photographer, bartender, engineer
4 different pets are kept: dog, horse, lizard, mouse
 1. the owner of the lizard is on the left or right of the person who likes brown##3
 2. the teacher is on the far left or far right##3
 3. the owner of the horse is on the right of the person who likes fuchsia##1
 4. the bartender is between the person who likes fuchsia and the person who likes lavender##2
 5. the owner of the mouse is on the left or right of the person who likes fuchsia##3
 6. the owner of the mouse is the person who likes brown##1
 7. the engineer is on the far right##1
 8. the person who likes lavender is in an odd position##4
 9. the photographer is between the person who likes mauve and the person who likes brown##2
10. the owner of the lizard is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Color   | lavender  | brown    | fuchsia | mauve    |
| Job   | teacher | bartender | photographer  | engineer |
| Pet           | lizard   | mouse    | dog        | horse   |

