.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-11::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, almond-milk, juice, soy-milk
4 different pets are kept: ferret, dog, mouse, cat
There 4 different types of food: papaya, kale, blueberry, onion
1. the person drinking 7up is on the far left or far right##3
2. the owner of the dog is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
3. the person eating onion is on the left or right of the owner of the mouse##3
4. the owner of the dog is in an even position##4
5. the person drinking juice is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1
6. the person eating onion is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
7. the person eating kale is on the left of the owner of the dog##1
8. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the person eating kale##3
9. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person eating papaya##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Beverage      | 7up                | soy-milk  | almond-milk | juice   |
| Pet           | cat | dog | ferret   | mouse |
| Food   | kale         | papaya     | onion     | blueberry |

