.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-12::.
4 different games are played: chess, monopoly, scrabble, poker
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, musical, romance, western
There are 4 different favourite colors: yellow, orange, red, azure
1. the person playing monopoly is on the left of the person playing poker##1
2. the person playing scrabble is on the far left##1
3. the person who likes orange is on the left or right of the person who likes azure##3
4. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the person watching musical movies##1
5. the person who likes yellow is between the person watching western movies and the person who likes azure##2
6. the person watching romance movies is in an even position##4
7. the person playing chess is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |   3    |    4    |
| Game          | scrabble    | monopoly  | poker  | chess |
| Movie-Genre   | western | musical | action | romance |
| Color   | red    | yellow     | azure    | orange |

