.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-13::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, house, funk, trance
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, australian, pakistani, turkish
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: daffodil, begonia, lily, zinnia
1. the person who growsbegonia is between the fan of funk and the argentine##2
2. the fan of ambient is on the far left or far right##3
3. the pakistani is on the left or right of the person who growslily##3
4. the person who growszinnia is on the left of the australian##1
5. the person who growszinnia is in an odd position##4
6. the fan of house is on the left or right of the person who growslily##3
7. the argentine is on the left or right of the turkish##3
8. the pakistani is the fan of ambient##1
9. the turkish is between the person who growslily and the person who growsdaffodil##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3    |     4     |
| Music-Genre      | ambient | funk      | house  | trance    |
| Nationality   | pakistani   | australian | turkish | argentine |
| Flower           | zinnia      | lily       | begonia   | daffodil      |

