.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-14::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: romance, crime, family, scientific
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, indian, indonesian, japanese
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, siglo, dannemann, pall-mall
1. the person watching family movies is in an even position##4
2. the person watching crime movies is between the person watching scientific movies and the aristoff-smoker##2
3. the siglo-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person watching scientific movies is in an even position##4
5. the aristoff-smoker is on the right of the dannemann-smoker##1
6. the japanese is between the aristoff-smoker and the australian##2
7. the siglo-smoker is on the far right##1
8. the indian is in an even position##4
9. the aristoff-smoker is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |    3     |     4      |
| Movie-Genre         | romance    | family | crime  | scientific  |
| Nationality   | indonesian | indian       | japanese | australian |
| Cigar         | dannemann   | aristoff      | pall-mall | siglo       |

