There 4 different types of food: lettuce, corn, cranberry, mango
4 different pets are kept: cat, guinea-pig, hamster, lizard
1. the owner of the guinea-pig is in an even position##4
2. the owner of the guinea-pig is the writer##1
3. the writer is on the left of the person eating corn##1
4. the dressmaker is the person eating mango##1
5. the dressmaker is on the far left##1
6. the person eating lettuce is the owner of the guinea-pig##1
7. the owner of the cat is on the left of the accountant##1
8. the owner of the lizard is the accountant##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3    |   4    |
| Job      | dressmaker      | writer | bartender     | accountant    |
| Food   | mango | lettuce      | corn | cranberry |
| Pet           | hamster   | guinea-pig  | cat     | lizard |

