.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-16::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, milk, mirinda, tea
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: punk, ambient, reggae, house
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: spy, fantasy, horror, superhero
1. the person drinking cola is on the left or right of the person drinking milk##3
2. the fan of punk is in an even position##4
3. the person watching superhero movies is on the far left##1
4. the fan of ambient is on the left or right of the person drinking tea##3
5. the person drinking milk is between the person watching fantasy movies and the fan of reggae##2
6. the person watching spy movies is the fan of house##1
7. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
8. the fan of punk is on the left of the person drinking cola##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Beverage    | mirinda    | milk     | cola    | tea        |
| Music-Genre       | reggae   | punk | ambient | house |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero | horror      | fantasy    | spy   |

