4. the person eating grapefruit is on the far left or far right##3
5. the owner of the goat is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
6. the person eating grapefruit is in an odd position##4
7. the owner of the goldfish is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person eating tomato is the fan of folk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |     3     |    4     |
