.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-20::.
There 4 different types of food: apple, broccoli, lime, pomegranate
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: sunflower, zinnia, lily, azalea
House: craftsman, farmhouse, gothic-revival, palace
1. the person eating apple is in an odd position##4
2. the person who growsazalea is in an odd position##4
3. the craftsman house is on the left or right of the person who growssunflower##3
4. the person eating lime is on the far left##1
5. the person eating broccoli is between the person who growsazalea and the person who growssunflower##2
6. the person who growszinnia is on the left of the person who growssunflower##1
7. the gothic-revival house is on the right of the person eating apple##1
8. the farmhouse house is on the left of the person eating broccoli##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2      |   3    |      4      |
| Food    | lime    | broccoli    | apple  | pomegranate |
| Flower   | azalea | zinnia | sunflower | lily      |
| House     | farmhouse   | craftsman        | palace   | gothic-revival       |

 